title: Python Pro-Clean Aquarium Gravel Washer/Siphon Kit, Large with Siphon Squeeze
feature: Includes the Python Squeeze Siphon Starter
Effectively separates and removes debris from your aquarium
Constructed with flexible, high quality tubing
For aquariums from 20 to 55 gallons in size
description: The Python Pro-Clean Gravel Washer & Siphon Kit is perfect for the beginner and experienced hobbyist alike. It effectively separates and removes debris from your aquarium while you perform routine water changes. This special kit also includes the Python Squeeze Siphon Starter. This handy accessory eliminates the need to start a siphon with your mouth. The Python Pro-Clean and Squeeze accessory are both constructed using only the highest quality materials. The large size is ideal for aquariums from 20 to 55 gallons in size.
